00:02:04.457 --> 00:02:06.025 line:95%,end
JILL: It was a mistake.

00:02:06.092 --> 00:02:09.696 line:95%,end
And I would really like for you
to find a spot for Kendall

00:02:09.762 --> 00:02:11.531 line:95%,end
on this team, like you did once before.
I know--

00:02:11.598 --> 00:02:13.099 line:95%,end
ABBY: Jill, I don't have time
