right in this group.

00:02:19.672 --> 00:02:20.807 line:95%,end
-ABBY: Kendall--
-JILL: She did it once before.

00:02:20.874 --> 00:02:22.208 line:95%,end
She can do it, again.

00:02:22.275 --> 00:02:24.644 line:5%,start
CHRISTI: I guess Candy Apples
just didn't give Jill what she wanted,

00:02:24.711 --> 00:02:27.013 line:5%,start
you know, a starring role in every number,

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:29.182 line:5%,start
a featured spot, a special part.

00:02:29.249 --> 00:02:31.818 line:95%,end
So here she is, hop, hop, hop, hopping

00:02:31.885 --> 00:02:33.853 line:95%,end
right back to the Abby Lee Dance Company.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:35.588 line:95%,end
You are off your rocker.

00:02:35.655 --> 00:02:37.724 line:95%,end
JILL: All I want
is what's best for Kendall.

00:02:37.790 --> 00:02:40.260 line:95%,end
Hey, I wanted
what was best for Kendall,

00:02:40.326 --> 00:02:42.028 line:95%,end
and you didn't give me time to do that.

00:02:42.095 --> 00:02:43.796 line:95%,end
-I know I made a mistake.
-ABBY: You should be--

00:02:43.863 --> 00:02:45.098 line:95%,end
-I'll pack my bags...
-ABBY: The reason I did this--

00:02:45.165 --> 00:02:46.533 line:95%,end
...and go home right now.

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:49.369 line:95%,end
Is that--would that make you guys
all really happy?

00:02:49.435 --> 00:02:51.070 line:95%,end
No. That will not make me happy.

00:02:51.137 --> 00:02:52.272 line:95%,end
Because that's what I'm doing!

00:02:52.338 --> 00:02:54.140 line:95%,end
-ABBY: And you know who's going to lose?
-I'm sick of this (bleep)!

00:02:57.343 --> 00:03:00.346 line:95%,end
Are you going to turn my child away
knowing she's got talent

00:03:00.413 --> 00:03:01.781 line:95%,end
and she belongs in this group?

00:03:01.848 --> 00:03:02.916 line:95%,end
I'm in the middle of a rehearsal!

00:03:02.982 --> 00:03:04.083 line:95%,end
Right. You know what? Rehearse.

00:03:04.150 --> 00:03:05.885 line:95%,end
I cannot believe this.

00:03:05.952 --> 00:03:07.387 line:95%,end
<i>I am literally speechless.</i>

00:03:07.453 --> 00:03:10.657 line:5%,start
Jill came in with a hot new hairdo

00:03:10.723 --> 00:03:14.294 line:5%,start
and a whole new wardrobe,
but it's still the same old Jill.

00:03:15.762 --> 00:03:17.030 line:95%,end
You know what, Abby?

00:03:17.096 --> 00:03:18.998 line:95%,end
Here. You hold your picture.

00:03:19.065 --> 00:03:21.334 line:95%,end
She deserves to be on that pyramid.

00:03:21.401 --> 00:03:23.069 line:95%,end
KELLY: <i>Who walks into pyramid,</i>

00:03:23.136 --> 00:03:25.305 line:5%,start
right in the middle,
and just shoves their kid in there?

00:03:25.371 --> 00:03:27.040 line:95%,end
<i>I think it's totally desperate.</i>

00:03:27.106 --> 00:03:28.174 line:95%,end
-ABBY: Girls!
-JILL: You go on.

00:03:28.241 --> 00:03:31.010 line:95%,end
ABBY: Girls, this is not about friends.

00:03:31.077 --> 00:03:33.413 line:95%,end
Do you want to see Kendall?
Invite her to your house.

00:03:33.479 --> 00:03:35.248 line:95%,end
This is my business.

00:03:35.315 --> 00:03:37.183 line:95%,end
Can you find it in your heart
to allow Kendall...

00:03:37.250 --> 00:03:38.918 line:95%,end
-Jill.
-JILL: ...to be a part of this team?

00:03:38.985 --> 00:03:40.853 line:95%,end
Jill, I will be glad to talk to you
at a later date.

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:41.754 line:95%,end
Okay.

00:03:41.821 --> 00:03:43.056 line:95%,end
ABBY: <i>I am furious with Jill.</i>

00:03:43.122 --> 00:03:45.625 line:95%,end
How she thinks
she's going to walk back in here

00:03:45.692 --> 00:03:47.293 line:95%,end
and get this kid back on the team,

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.996 line:95%,end
<i>it's not this girl's fault.</i>
<i>She's a great dancer.</i>

00:03:50.063 --> 00:03:50.997 line:95%,end
<i>Let her rehearse.</i>

00:03:51.064 --> 00:03:52.265 line:95%,end
<i>Stick her on the end.</i>

00:03:52.332 --> 00:03:53.399 line:95%,end
<i>It's not a big deal.</i>

00:03:53.466 --> 00:03:56.302 line:95%,end
Now, we're going
to Starpower in Lancaster.

00:03:56.369 --> 00:03:59.606 line:95%,end
Not very far, but a big competition.

00:03:59.672 --> 00:04:02.275 line:95%,end
Lots of people from New Jersey
and the New York area

00:04:02.342 --> 00:04:03.910 line:95%,end
