00:04:03.977 --> 00:04:05.044 line:95%,end
<i>It's a really big deal.</i>

00:04:05.111 --> 00:04:07.580 line:95%,end
They enter 50, 60 numbers.

00:04:07.647 --> 00:04:09.215 line:95%,end
We're going with one group.

00:04:10.049 --> 00:04:11.251 line:95%,end
Moving on to the pyramid--

00:04:11.317 --> 00:04:14.387 line:95%,end
on the bottom of the pyramid,
Mackenzie.

00:04:14.454 --> 00:04:16.389 line:95%,end
When things are done
in "The Contagion"

00:04:16.456 --> 00:04:19.592 line:95%,end
<i>and you do it first</i>
<i>and then Paige and then Nia,</i>

00:04:19.659 --> 00:04:20.893 line:95%,end
when you do it so fast,

00:04:20.960 --> 00:04:23.129 line:95%,end
you make Paige and Nia look like
they're off,

00:04:23.196 --> 00:04:25.031 line:95%,end
like they're the ones that are wrong.

00:04:25.098 --> 00:04:27.567 line:95%,end
Next, Nia.

00:04:27.634 --> 00:04:30.536 line:95%,end
The area walkover got you into trouble.

00:04:30.603 --> 00:04:32.138 line:95%,end
<i>Don't let it happen again.</i>

00:04:32.205 --> 00:04:33.773 line:95%,end
You need to slow down.

00:04:35.041 --> 00:04:38.878 line:95%,end
Paige, you really didn't do anything wrong
but you're part of the trio,

00:04:38.945 --> 00:04:41.547 line:95%,end
so you have to take responsibility for it.

00:04:42.382 --> 00:04:43.750 line:95%,end
Chloe.

00:04:43.816 --> 00:04:47.353 line:95%,end
Chloe, it was good
but you get into those categories

00:04:47.420 --> 00:04:49.355 line:95%,end
with 11 and 12-year-olds,

00:04:49.422 --> 00:04:52.959 line:95%,end
and you never get up there
where I think you belong.

00:04:53.026 --> 00:04:56.296 line:95%,end
Next, I have Brooke.

00:04:56.362 --> 00:04:59.232 line:95%,end
Brooke, you did a great job.

00:04:59.299 --> 00:05:00.500 line:95%,end
Your technique was clean.

00:05:00.566 --> 00:05:02.101 line:95%,end
<i>From where I was sitting,</i>

00:05:02.168 --> 00:05:04.671 line:95%,end
<i>I thought your facial expressions</i>
<i>were wonderful.</i>

00:05:04.737 --> 00:05:06.406 line:95%,end
I thought you were outstanding.

00:05:06.472 --> 00:05:09.876 line:95%,end
And on top of the pyramid, Maddie.

00:05:09.942 --> 00:05:11.577 line:95%,end
You went out there in "9:00 to 12:00"

00:05:11.644 --> 00:05:13.813 line:95%,end
