00:05:13.880 --> 00:05:15.581 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: <i>Maddie wins all the time,</i>

00:05:15.648 --> 00:05:18.418 line:95%,end
<i>and it's not that we're jealous</i>
<i>of Maddie's victories.</i>

00:05:18.484 --> 00:05:21.754 line:95%,end
<i>I would never rub Chloe's victories</i>

00:05:21.821 --> 00:05:23.056 line:95%,end
<i>in anyone else's faces.</i>

00:05:23.122 --> 00:05:25.992 line:95%,end
