00:07:42.495 --> 00:07:44.430 line:95%,end
Because that's unexpected, to me.

00:07:44.497 --> 00:07:45.565 line:95%,end
JILL: <i>She wouldn't talk to me.</i>

00:07:45.631 --> 00:07:47.099 line:95%,end
<i>I said, we--can we--can we talk?</i>

00:07:47.166 --> 00:07:48.067 line:95%,end
KELLY: <i>What's there to talk about?</i>

00:07:48.134 --> 00:07:49.502 line:95%,end
